snippet.title: Default Dan Trailer!
snippet.description: Default Dan is a casual platformer coming to desktop and mobile platforms. Everything you think you know about platforming mechanics is flipped upside down, requiring you to fight your gaming instincts to survive. Avoid coins, jump on spikes, and defeat the princess in this lighthearted indie platformer.
